window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Jasmine and her grandmother are reunited, which means only one thing lies ahead:</p> <p>Her two worlds will unite.</p> <p>After years of rumor and hearsay, Jasmine comes face-to-face with the very thing her mother warned her about: her werewolf.</p> <p>There's only one way to move forward and find her target.</p> <p>It won't be easy, but Jasmine must be initiated and earn her rightful place.</p> <p>Along the way, she is guided and hindered by strange forest creatures, as well as a neighboring mob who have heard about Jasmine's powers.</p> <p>It all comes down to a showdown when old friends appear and unruly creatures raise their necrotic heads to the world.</p>"; 
